    Black Aracnia held her bowcaster level with Quickstrike, following his 
every move. She was very suspicious of the situation, and had alot to deal 
with right now. She was the lone defender of the ship presently, Megatron and 
his goons were trying to get in, and she had to deal with that vermine trying 
to get in. The best bet at the moment was to stun him and place him in the 
Brig.
    "Sorry Quicky, I cant let you waltz around, not just yet at least. But, 
belive me, I do apprechiate the offer." Aracnia said with her evil smile.
    Then, with the pull of the trigger, she fired a missle arrow from er 
bowcaster at Quickstrike, programmed to knock him out for an hour or so. It 
would give her time to settle things.
